space

Class Space

  • java.lang.Object
    • space.Space
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BridgeSpace, CaptureCornerSpace, HoleCovered, IndoorPath, IndoorPathSpace, IndoorWallSpace, IndoorWastelandSpace, MountainSpace, PathSpace, TowerSpace, WallSpace, WastelandSpace, WaterSpace

    public abstract class Space
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The abstract space class. Is used to easily create any amount of different types of spaces. Holds all of a spaces information to allow easy addition of new spaces.
